					<description><![CDATA[<div style="margin: 5px 5% 10px 5%;"><img src="https://gaminggadgets.de/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/ubisoft-logo.jpg" width="1195" height="670" title="" alt="ubisoft logo" /></div>
<div>
<div style="margin-bottom:20px;"><img width="1195" height="670" src="https://gaminggadgets.de/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/ubisoft-logo.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="ubisoft logo" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://gaminggadgets.de/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/ubisoft-logo.jpg 1195w, https://gaminggadgets.de/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/ubisoft-logo-300x168.jpg 300w, https://gaminggadgets.de/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/ubisoft-logo-1024x574.jpg 1024w, https://gaminggadgets.de/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/ubisoft-logo-768x431.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1195px) 100vw, 1195px" /></div>
